{"tid":1559123,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"各位北角街坊 係時候光復北角連儂牆","createTime":"2019-09-10T16:31:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T20:14:11.000Z","uid":146505,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"80d761310e746276336a86adeeed5cdec83e1ca7","tid":1559123,"uid":146505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T16:31:17.000Z","msg":"光復北角<br />\n對抗福獨份子<br />\n<br />\n第一步整翻好天橋個連儂牆先<br />\n屌你老母福獨狗撕紙就勁<br />\n我哋玩鎖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/idNzqWe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FidNzqWe.jpg&h=eb137626&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鎖撚到好似人地嗰啲情侶許願牆咁<br />\n睇你班福獨佬點拆<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二步可以開個tg group報下現況<br />\n有咩事例如又人打翻屋企嘅手足時<br />\n真係要一齊落去幫拖<br />\n<br />\n據以前經驗佢哋好撚蠢 <br />\n打完一個仲會企定定等<br />\n想打多幾個咁<br />\n其實佢哋人真係唔多<br />\n而且好撚笨柒<br />\n肥佬居多<br />\n<br />\n睇情況如果唔正面硬拼的話<br />\n可以做啲暗面嘢<br />\n搞下佢哋啲舖頭之類<br />\n好多福獨狗喺北角都有自己生意/同鄉會/樓上佛堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">支線任一樣要做<br />\n有仇不報非君子</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咪撚俾班福獨佬以為北角係佢哋嘅</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2ac73216f3d2420df831415159697c0407ade83","tid":1559123,"uid":146505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T16:31: